snippet.title: Indians And Diwali | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys
Happy Diwali to all of you , may this diwali brings joy , laughter , prosperity 

As the Title is Indians And Diwali this Video has everything that happens during Diwali Festival . The most relatable and Funny Diwali Video . Scenarios like what happens on Indian families doing Diwali shopping for dhanteras shopping new utensils or jewellery shopping of gold coin , silver coin from brand like Tanishq . Kaamwali and her struggles with house cleaning waiting for diwali gifts , diwali bonus . Daughter painting diya and mom hanging diwali lights . Girls dressing up in traditional dieting whole month to look good and clicking pictures and making videos . Preparations for office diwali pooja , sisters cleaning house and competing and having fun , next day of diwali and taking off the lights , flower garlands , rangoli , giving diwali to staff , guards , kaamwali bai , Aunties for shopping for diwali pooja kheel patashe , patisha , paan , supari , sweets , favourite mathai moti choor ladoo , kaju ki barfi , bondi ke laddoo , cham cham , diwali decoration , bhandan var , diya , lights , candles , rangoli , diwali gifts dry fruits , gift box . Indian Aunties bargaining with shopkeeper , shops making huge profits during diwali dhamaka sales , going out to relatives to wish happy diwali and dealing with diwali 2024 traffic jams , giving gifts to relatives and travelling in car , indian sweets shops fully loaded with customers , eating in restaurants after diwali shopping , shopkeeper selling bandhanbar , latkane , diwali decorations , eating dosa , chowmein , work from home people busy with job and ghar ki safai , tuition mam helps kids prepare their diwali poem , diwali essay , teaching why diwali is celebrated , diwali school function costumes , diwali is the festival food , every foodie loves puri , mathi , samosa , ladoo , aloo , kheer , halwa , muli ki bhujji , raita , achar , panchamrit , laxmi ganesh pooja , house aura cleansing with diwali aarti , talking about the ban on fire crackers , diwali away from home , pg wali diwali , showing off chandi , gold gifts , buying air purifier cause of the air pollution and noise pullution caused by crackers in delhi , south delhi posh diwali partiers playing poker , drinking , tambola , diwali vlogs , diwali outfits , lehenga , suits , saree , kurti , kurta , and looking beautiful and clicking pictures . West Delhi people mocking south delhi on dieting on diwali doing keto , intermittent fasting or just drinking alcohol , many more fun things covered in the diwali video .
This video is filled with Festive season memories and situations we all have been in . 
Relish and Relive your Childhood Memories of Diwali festival
Do share it with your friends and family , Relatives , Neighbour . A very happy diwali 2024 season to all of you and Happy deepawali  .. Comment down your Fav Part , 
Like , Share and 
Subscribe to our Channel - http://bit.ly/thepaayaljain | Press Bell Icon

Tena Jaiin : https://www.instagram.com/tenajaiin/?...

snippet.title: We Built a BIG HOUSE in Minecraft üòç
snippet.description:
Today I will build House in Minecraft with my wife  @urmilaaa    Yes Husband Wife Minecraft is back :) We are going to have super fun in this Minecraft Hindi Series!

Me and Urmila Search for Items and Villages in Minecraft. Oh! Search se yaad aya...try Circle to Search in Android! 
Circle, highlight, scribble, or tap text or images anywhere on your screen to select and search for them on Google.
Happy to be part of Team Android :) Excited to Play Minecraft Pocket Edition on my Android Phone.

Today we explore in Minecraft World and start build our Big house and Wheat Farm! Can Urmila Fight Creepers, Zombies in Minecraft? I also fight pillagers today and we build our bedroom, kitchen and cook Food. Hope you enjoy this Funny Minecraft Story Gameplay Series with @Mythpat and @urmilaaa  in Hindi.

my insta - https://www.instagram.com/mythpat

#minecraft #mythpat

snippet.title: MIXTURE Snack | DIWALI Special Traditional Mixture Recipe Cooking In Village | South Indian Snacks
snippet.description:
Mixture Recipe is a popular snack recipe in South India, especially in Tamil Nadu, Kerala and Karnataka. Today, we are cooking this recipe as a Diwali Special. The specialty of this snack is its mixed taste. 

To enhance the flavor of this mixture, we use Boondi, Fried Nuts, Fried Spices, and other healthy ingredients, along with Omappodi.

The taste is memorable!

Today I am going to share you a popular Indian sweet motichur laddu recipe on the occasion of Diwali. Motichur Laddu is Originating in North India, Motichur Laddu is traditionally made during festivals and celebrations, like Diwali, weddings, and other joyous occasions, making it a beloved delicacy across India. Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainment‚Äôs mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznavi‚Äôs love?

About The Episode 

This Diwali, get ready for a romantic comedy ride with Episode 1 of Wrong Number Reboot! 
Mihir finds himself inundated with calls for Adhira, a singer who unknowingly shares her old number, leading to hilarious situations and unexpected chemistry. With the help of his lively friend PPT, this episode promises fun and sparks! 
Watch the full episode now!

Series Overview 

"Wrong Number Reboot" kicks off with Mihir's life turning upside down when he starts receiving endless calls meant for Adhira, a rising singer who unknowingly gives out his number to her fans. With his lively friend PPT by his side, Mihir tries to manage the chaos. Meanwhile, Adhira is navigating her own world with the help of her close friend, Manasi. Things take a twist when Rohan enters the scene, bringing new challenges to their lives. To set things straight, PPT brings in the fan-favorite mastermind, Badri.
Get ready for a fun-filled ride of comedy, romance, and unexpected surprises!

Join our team of writers as they toss around the most outlandish, over-the-top, and downright ridiculous ideas for the ultimate Diwali-themed video. snippet.title: Drop the Beat | MTV Hustle 4
snippet.description:
Drop the Beat is an electrifying rap where participants, squad bosses, and judges come together to perform as one, creating an unforgettable experience. With everyone bringing their unique style and energy, the track turns into a high-energy celebration, blending voices, beats, and camaraderie for a blast that embodies unity and pure hip-hop joy.



Song Credits
Track Name: Drop the Beat
Written & Performed By: 99side, Dharmik, Pho, Vichaar, K!LLSWITCH, Ghaint Jxtt,  Siyaahi, Little Bhatia, Naam Sujal, Ajitesh Bhati, Danish, Devil The Rhymer, Sense, Rajjo, Mad Trip,LashcurryRaga, Dino, Dee MC,EPR, Ikka, Raftaar

Music Producer: Aditya Pushkarna, 
Primary Artist: 99side, Dharmik, Pho, Vichaar, K!LLSWITCH, Ghaint Jxtt,  Siyaahi, Little Bhatia, Naam Sujal, Ajitesh Bhati, Danish, Devil The Rhymer, Sense, Rajjo, Mad Trip,Lashcurry, Raga, Dino, Dee MC,EPR, Ikka, Raftaar

snippet.title: Thozha - Back to Back comedy scene 2 | Karthi | Nagarjuna | Vivek | Tammanah | Adithya TV
snippet.description:
The story revolves around Vikramadhitya (Nagarjuna) a quadriplegic billionaire, and Seenu, (Karthi) his ex-convict caretaker. Circumstances in their life teach them the value of relationships over money. 

Thozha is a 2016 movie . It was released in both Telugu and Tamil languages. Its name in Telugu is Oppri . The film is a remake of the French film The Intouchables . The film stars Karthik Sivakumar , Nagarsuna , Tamannaah , Prakasu Rasu , Vivek , Anushka , Seyashuda , Sireyya . The film is directed by Vamsi Baidipalli and produced by Prasad V Potluri.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant.
